---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — changebrief" description="How changebrief collects, uses, and protects your data." lang="en">
  <Header lang="en" />
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-32 pb-24 animate-fade-in-up">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight theme-text mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="theme-text-muted text-sm mb-12">Last updated: March 29, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose-custom space-y-8 text-sm theme-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold theme-text mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
        <p>changebrief is operated by Kristian Wigander as a sole proprietorship based in Sweden. Contact: <a href="mailto:kristian@changebrief.io" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-400">kristian@changebrief.io</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold theme-text mb-3">2. What data we collect</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5">
          <li><strong>Account data:</strong> Email address, name, and profile image from your OAuth provider (Google or GitHub).</li>
          <li><strong>Monitoring data:</strong> URLs you add, screenshots of those pages, AI-generated change summaries, and your review actions.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Basic analytics (page views, feature usage) to improve the service. No third-party trackers.</li>
          <li><strong>Payment data:</strong> Handled entirely by Polar/Stripe. We never see or store your card details.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold theme-text mb-3">3. How we use your data</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5">
          <li>To provide the monitoring service (screenshots, AI analysis, notifications).</li>
          <li>To send you email notifications and digest reports you have opted into.</li>
          <li>To improve the service based on aggregated, anonymized usage patterns.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold theme-text mb-3">4. Third-party processors</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5">
          <li><strong>OpenAI</strong> — AI analysis of screenshots (images sent via API, not stored by OpenAI per their data usage policy).</li>
          <li><strong>Turso</strong> — Database hosting (EU, AWS eu-west-1, Ireland).</li>
          <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — Application hosting (edge network, EU-first routing).</li>
          <li><strong>Resend</strong> — Transactional email delivery.</li>
          <li><strong>Polar/Stripe</strong> — Payment processing.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold theme-text mb-3">5. Data storage & security</h2>
        <p>All data is stored within the EU (AWS eu-west-1, Ireland). Data is encrypted in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest (AES-256). Access to production systems is restricted to the service operator.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold theme-text mb-3">6. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5">
          <li><strong>Access</strong> — Request a copy of all data we hold about you.</li>
          <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — Correct inaccurate data.</li>
          <li><strong>Erasure</strong> — Request deletion of your account and all associated data.</li>
          <li><strong>Portability</strong> — Export your data in CSV format (available in the dashboard).</li>
          <li><strong>Object</strong> — Object to processing of your data.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">To exercise any of these rights, contact <a href="mailto:kristian@changebrief.io" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-400">kristian@changebrief.io</a>. We respond within 30 days.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold theme-text mb-3">7. Data retention</h2>
        <p>Change history is retained according to your plan (7 days to 1 year). When you delete your account, all data is permanently removed within 30 days.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold theme-text mb-3">8. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use only essential cookies: authentication session, language preference, and theme preference. No advertising or tracking cookies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold theme-text mb-3">9. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy occasionally. Material changes will be communicated via email to registered users. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</Base>
